It is possible to use a block partitioned matrix product that involves only algebra on submatrices of the factors. The partitioning of the factors is not arbitrary, however, and requires &quot;conformable partitions&quot; between two matrices formula_20 and formula_59 such that all submatrix products that will be used are defined.
