:&quot;3) Non-Italicized channel numbers indicate the RF channel in current use for digital (ATSC) transmission as allocated by the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission.&quot;

===Owned-and-operated stations===

===Secondary carriers===
These stations are also owned and operated by Bell Media and carry most CTV 2 programming, but are locally branded.


